==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Quadrivial
<hw>Quad*riv"i*al</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the four
⟦ldquo⟧liberal arts⟦rdquo⟧ making up the quadrivium.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadrivium</ent>⟦br⟧
